<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 01:08:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：检查员称比亚迪以非正常签证将数百名中国工人带到巴西</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/byd-brought-hundreds-chinese-workers-brazil-irregular-visas-inspector-2025-01-08/</link><description>一位重要的劳工监察员周二告诉路透社，电动汽车生产商比亚迪带着数百名持非正常签证的中国工人在巴西建厂，并补充说该公司已承诺对留在该国的工人遵守当地劳动法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/byd-brought-hundreds-chinese-workers-brazil-irregular-visas-inspector-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>西藏地震造成120多人死亡，救援工作正在进行中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rescue-efforts-under-way-after-earthquake-tibet-kills-more-than-120-2025-01-08/</link><description>中国当局表示，周二喜马拉雅山麓强烈地震中被困的 400 多人已获救，3 万多名居民已被重新安置，救援人员仍在继续搜寻幸存者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rescue-efforts-under-way-after-earthquake-tibet-kills-more-than-120-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿对中国宁德时代的标签可能会对特斯拉产生怎样的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-washingtons-tag-chinas-catl-could-affect-tesla-2025-01-07/</link><description>华盛顿将宁德时代列入与中国军方合作的公司名单，这可能会让特斯拉创始人埃隆·马斯克陷入困境，挑战他如何平衡自己在特朗普政府中的角色与与中国的关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 23:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-washingtons-tag-chinas-catl-could-affect-tesla-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：收益率飙升打击风险偏好，日本对日元发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2025-01-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 21:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>科技组织敦促美国停止限制全球获取人工智能芯片的规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tech-group-urges-us-halt-rule-that-would-limit-global-access-ai-chips-2025-01-07/</link><description>一个科技行业组织周二敦促总统乔·拜登政府不要在最后一刻发布控制全球人工智能芯片获取的规则，并警告称这些限制将危及美国在人工智能领域的领导地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 19:36:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tech-group-urges-us-halt-rule-that-would-limit-global-access-ai-chips-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>Itau BBA 表示，亚马逊和 MercadoLibre 将从墨西哥进口关税中受益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/amazon-mercadolibre-benefit-mexico-import-tariffs-itau-bba-says-2025-01-07/</link><description>Itau BBA 的分析师表示，相对于 Shein 和 Temu 等亚洲零售商，电子商务巨头亚马逊和 MercadoLibre 将从墨西哥低成本进口商品新关税中受益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 18:56:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/amazon-mercadolibre-benefit-mexico-import-tariffs-itau-bba-says-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>赫斯首席执行官对石油需求持乐观态度，称圭亚那的潜力几乎没有发挥</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/hess-ceo-offers-upbeat-oil-demand-forecast-says-guyanas-potential-barely-2025-01-07/</link><description>Hess首席执行官约翰·赫斯(John Hess)周二表示，尽管对中国的需求以及美国和非欧佩克产油国产量增加感到担忧，但他认为今年石油市场更接近平衡，而不是供应过剩。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/hess-ceo-offers-upbeat-oil-demand-forecast-says-guyanas-potential-barely-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>谢因对中国棉花使用保持沉默，让英国立法者对供应链一无所知</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-representative-declines-say-if-company-uses-cotton-china-uk-hearing-2025-01-07/</link><description>周二，当英国议会委员会询问这家在线快时尚零售商是否使用来自中国或新疆省的棉花时，Shein 的代表拒绝提供直接答案，这对于担心其供应链的潜在投资者来说是一个关键问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:25:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-representative-declines-say-if-company-uses-cotton-china-uk-hearing-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>据 Telegraaf 报道，飞利浦出售小型芯片制造子公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/philips-sells-small-chipmaking-subsidiary-telegraaf-reports-2025-01-07/</link><description>据 Telegraaf 报纸援引 Xiver 首席执行官的话说，医疗保健技术公司飞利浦已出售其 Xiver 计算机芯片子公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 14:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/philips-sells-small-chipmaking-subsidiary-telegraaf-reports-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>西藏地震多发区发生震颤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tremors-earthquake-prone-tibet-2025-01-07/</link><description>西藏是地震活跃区，去年发生了100多起3.0级以上的地震。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 12:14:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tremors-earthquake-prone-tibet-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商将与特斯拉、Polestar 合并二氧化碳排放量，以满足欧盟 2025 年规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-toyota-ford-mazda-subaru-plan-pool-co2-emissions-with-tesla-2025-01-07/</link><description>电动汽车销量较低的公司可以与细分市场的领导者“汇集”其排放量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-toyota-ford-mazda-subaru-plan-pool-co2-emissions-with-tesla-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美国对中国无人机存在安全风险的怀疑是“不负责任的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-us-suspicion-security-risks-chinese-drones-is-irresponsible-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，中国称美国“毫无根据地怀疑”中国无人机系统存在信息安全风险，“极其不负责任”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-us-suspicion-security-risks-chinese-drones-is-irresponsible-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：市场现实的震撼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-07/</link><description>阿曼达·库珀 (Amanda Cooper) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国奇瑞报告2024年销量增长38.4%至260万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-reports-384-jump-2024-sales-26-mln-vehicles-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国汽车制造商奇瑞 (CHERY.UL) 周二报告称，2024 年全球汽车销量将增长 38.4%，达到 260 万辆，并预计今年销量将超过 300 万辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 10:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-reports-384-jump-2024-sales-26-mln-vehicles-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>韩国被弹劾的领导人尹正蹲在首尔的“比佛利山庄”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-impeached-leader-yoon-hunkers-down-seouls-beverly-hills-2025-01-07/</link><description>周二，在调查人员计划逮捕他的同时，被弹劾的韩国总统尹锡烈和他的妻子、狗和猫仍然躲在一排排铁丝网和一小队个人保安后面，躲在他那座庞大的山坡别墅里。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 10:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-impeached-leader-yoon-hunkers-down-seouls-beverly-hills-2025-01-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>